---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Kaya Blue | Professional Web Agency" description="High-converting digital experiences for real estate, staffing, and finance professionals.">
<main class="flex-1">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative px-6 lg:px-20 py-20 lg:py-32 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 w-fit">
<span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent" style="">Premium Web Solutions</span>
</div>
<h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white" style="">
                            Websites that work as hard as <span class="text-accent" style="">your business</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl" style="">
                            We build high-converting digital experiences tailored for real estate, staffing, and finance professionals who demand excellence.
                        </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
<a href="/book-a-call" class="bg-accent text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-base hover:scale-105 transition-transform accent-glow">Book a Free Call</a>
<a href="/our-work" class="border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-base hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-card-dark transition-colors">View Our Work</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative group">
<div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent to-blue-500 rounded-xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000"></div>
<div class="relative aspect-video rounded-xl bg-slate-200 dark:bg-card-dark border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-800 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" data-alt="Modern laptop displaying a sleek dashboard interface" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAGolhYl_zdrOvS7TtUVLDM0I-HCOlGSD6qB1iN0ezkVznWtgHnKs4_noRPNypWEshOUpc0V0JkQ23KJNVFZabdT251YUto0EBiMbH64086P5gfU0UDyRDhGDyzUpgOknhdTMOI-k6tgFhmGSRSa3Kis_j6uSAX68wzdRz5RBN3L1pRg9EeJ8ZQcVyWZV54KVFPMuuZQx75xkfiAcEOOHltRfvdx67WuU_S4WzHIqu1Dxzseuy3c4L7OLcqBUeKIy3zl51hWZs2L-w" style=""/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Industries Section -->
<section class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#0d1b2a] py-24 px-6 lg:px-20">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="text-accent font-mono text-sm tracking-widest mb-4" style="">EXPERTISE</h2>
<h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold dark:text-white" style="">Industries We Serve</h3>
<div class="h-1 w-20 bg-accent mt-6 rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<!-- Real Estate -->
<div class="group p-8 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-card-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-accent/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm">
<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" style="">real_estate_agent</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 dark:text-white" style="">Real Estate</h4>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-text-muted leading-relaxed" style="">
                                High-impact property listings and automated lead generation funnels designed to close deals faster.
                            </p>
</div>
<!-- Staffing -->
<div class="group p-8 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-card-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-accent/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm">
<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" style="">group_work</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 dark:text-white" style="">Staffing Agencies</h4>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-text-muted leading-relaxed" style="">
                                Custom portals for recruitment and Uitzendbureaus, streamlining applicant tracking and client management.
                            </p>
</div>
<!-- Finance -->
<div class="group p-8 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-card-dark border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-accent/50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm">
<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" style="">account_balance</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 dark:text-white" style="">Finance</h4>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-text-muted leading-relaxed" style="">
                                Secure, professional, and compliant fintech solutions that build trust and drive complex user interactions.
                            </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Portfolio Section -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-16 gap-6">
<div>
<h2 class="text-accent font-mono text-sm tracking-widest mb-4" style="">PORTFOLIO</h2>
<h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold dark:text-white" style="">Our Recent Work</h3>
</div>
<a class="text-accent font-medium flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-4 transition-all group" href="/our-work">
                        View All Projects <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" style="">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<!-- Project 1 -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 group">
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl aspect-[4/3] bg-card-dark relative shadow-xl">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100" data-alt="Luxury real estate agency landing page design" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC629CWE8BoaBY1jVYT7NoANEc_i0P9q4_c0oWoRj9wxlLasno1LKZcAfe4KDHSVbwZY7h2TJHf8hw6gPXFxjs90zwWoSoMKVcm1Os9iq8KwrEpIruTcP_7IjMOMEohbJBjviiLIIySeDu-_cmjI4HBcH1x_vX3u39q04lz7gRzOdmYFXM-N6z-wVQ-wB49LMme2RTEkjjYGfyDHrCpz0nnXUDQ32_s-35EtRhTjFNeoxRWHGr7-ROWFFmYl2JzLc0zKFkQWZdXdh4" style=""/>
<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-primary/80 backdrop-blur-md px-3 py-1 rounded border border-accent/30">
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest text-accent uppercase" style="">Real Estate</span>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold dark:text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors" style="">Skyline Properties</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-text-muted" style="">Direct Booking &amp; CRM Integration</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Project 2 -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 group">
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl aspect-[4/3] bg-card-dark relative shadow-xl">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100" data-alt="Professional staffing portal dashboard view" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDSfoaB0IBygO-rYQJRBBDs01opJ0q7fSX3eHJris6Sriic-FbolTVnRspS-IRfD-Q24o2ssDECl0m3xzqpO2JQdpHzGd6JkAmL-pEIUEMy7Df_2LQjS9KjsBp3bdtNwGf-yygjKJFU_VGT6l2Z-9LwqQiQavQslAjuLot5UpCPC0tZS-Kz0LzzkPddcK2E5I0gZbybW9u7XbOztY_L37EL7S1jyzefPkFuBZtf8BXIU16EvQq_bc75vkW1qfd7XqhOwKng8Hca5W8" style=""/>
<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-primary/80 backdrop-blur-md px-3 py-1 rounded border border-accent/30">
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest text-accent uppercase" style="">Staffing</span>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold dark:text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors" style="">TalentFlow Portal</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-text-muted" style="">Bespoke Applicant Tracking System</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Project 3 -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 group">
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl aspect-[4/3] bg-card-dark relative shadow-xl">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100" data-alt="Modern financial advisor wealth management interface" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCmkP0AAkgYpC1P2Kw9iaqEJ-ZotIqx1LW3EkQCEqOpBEdNz6BvUn-jp28rTSi-nKOFHo6nkyoVWTHlTi3bkxjavnBl2F1k15B810LqXmJM76o-c0Jnwj9hMFB8KsRe72kFarUSA6Jo-QRKtX2ZzT0dBGV_and8GRB5FoHvHyJFlhdelIBV0Fa5AuHE1u76GyAGJuKc3wsUm6hKWTH17SVrNMlTzQiMbPSt0wNn4GoOjh0KYLHNfMFBVD8oZ-7ofklaZV1FkSE_4iE" style=""/>
<div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-primary/80 backdrop-blur-md px-3 py-1 rounded border border-accent/30">
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest text-accent uppercase" style="">Finance</span>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-lg font-bold dark:text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors" style="">Vantage Wealth</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-text-muted" style="">Secure Asset Tracking Platform</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Social Proof Section -->
<section class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-card-dark/30 py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 border-y border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div>
<h2 class="text-accent font-mono text-sm tracking-widest mb-4" style="">TESTIMONIALS</h2>
<h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold dark:text-white mb-8" style="">Trusted by industry leaders</h3>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="p-2 bg-accent/20 rounded text-accent"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="">star</span></div>
<div class="p-2 bg-accent/20 rounded text-accent"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="">star</span></div>
<div class="p-2 bg-accent/20 rounded text-accent"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="">star</span></div>
<div class="p-2 bg-accent/20 rounded text-accent"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="">star</span></div>
<div class="p-2 bg-accent/20 rounded text-accent"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="">star</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
<div class="p-8 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-card-dark border-l-4 border-accent shadow-sm italic">
<p class="text-lg dark:text-slate-200 mb-6" style="">"Kaya Blue transformed our outdated real estate site into a lead-generating machine. We saw a 40% increase in inquiries within the first month."</p>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 not-italic">
<div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></div>
<div>
<p class="font-bold dark:text-white" style="">Sarah Janssen</p>
<p class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-tighter" style="">CEO, Janssen Realty</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="p-8 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-card-dark border-l-4 border-accent shadow-sm italic">
<p class="text-lg dark:text-slate-200 mb-6" style="">"The recruitment portal built for our agency has saved us countless hours. Professional, fast, and exactly what we needed."</p>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 not-italic">
<div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></div>
<div>
<p class="font-bold dark:text-white" style="">Mark de Vries</p>
<p class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-tighter" style="">Founder, NextStep Staffing</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Call to Action -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
<div class="p-12 lg:p-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-card-dark to-primary border border-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -ml-20 -mb-20 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
<h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-6 dark:text-white" style="">Ready to scale your digital presence?</h2>
<p class="text-xl text-text-muted mb-10 leading-relaxed" style="">Let's discuss how a custom-built digital experience can drive real results for your business.</p>
<a href="/book-a-call" class="inline-block bg-accent text-primary px-10 py-5 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform accent-glow">Schedule Your Strategy Session</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</BaseLayout>
